。<br />\n<br />\nFrom明報"},{"pid":"fc2099f657ce9720652d571303c83943a23c3ffd","tid":2487691,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8522a504f3bca7c4639941498164e3607c5c6354","tid":2487691,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7bd537bbfed6a9a9731cd7f1fc41dc6698fcf9d2","tid":2487691,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25166ff79db20fa9d11150c6322ab1ac956fc99b","tid":2487691,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"但福島要倒30年，500萬公噸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"大亞灣例咗幾多年，幾多公噸，濃度幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"一般輕水式核反應堆在水冷過程中，也會產生含氚的核污水，處理後排入大海，確是常見做法。華府為日本排放福島核污水背書，一大理由正是「這類含氚水的排放是國際慣例，符合安全」，然而福島核災產生的污水，跟一般反應堆冷卻水，根本是兩碼子的事。布萊因稱，東電外泄的內部文件顯示，過濾系統未能徹底去除碘、釕、鍶、鈷等高輻射物質，有日本地方報章亦提過，有核污水樣本的釕106及碘129含量，超出可接受水平。綠色和平去年發表的報告還稱，ALPS設計上並未考慮去除半衰期長達5000年的碳-14放射性同位數，意味排放核污水可以遺禍數千年，並有可能損害人體DNA。<br />\n<br />\nFrom明報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">大亞灣</span></strong>三隻正體字唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a286cadc7e5c2e7f425d14e1787541655d84d9f","tid":2487691,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc6f45f20e3adc92131f4e7efee90ce616b0f5e","tid":2487691,"uid":198792,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"7d44e2b6979177e6e0503d0cc6762d7f2ef93979","tid":2487691,"uid":313162,"like":4,"dislike":37,"score":-33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"自己批准自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:45:34.000Z","msg":"日本的行動得到<span class=\"red\">國際原子能機構</span>支持，機構說日本政府的處理方法，與世